                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Effect</strong> The electrovore unleashes a shock wave that deals @Damage[2d6[electricity]|options:area-damage] damage to creatures in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] (@Check[reflex|dc:15]). It can't use Electrical Discharge again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Electrical Discharge]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes half damage. Items in its possession with the tech trait becomes glitching 1. If the target has the tech trait, it becomes @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Glitching]{Glitching 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but full damage and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Glitching]{Glitching 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As success, but double damage and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Glitching]{Glitching 3}.</p>"
